org.gvsig.fmap.dal

Interface DataServerExplorer

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DataFactoryUnit, Disposable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    DataServerExplorer_v2, DataServerExplorerProvider, DBServerExplorer, FilesystemServerExplorer, FilesystemServerExplorerProviderServices, JDBCServerExplorer, JDBCServerExplorer, RasterDataServerExplorer
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractDataServerExplorer, AbstractDBServerExplorer, DefaultFilesystemServerExplorer, GMLDataExplorer, JDBCServerExplorerBase, JDBCServerExplorerBase, MultiFileServerExplorer, OGRDataExplorer, PostGISRasterServerExplorer, TileServerExplorer, WCSServerExplorer, WFSServerExplorer, WMSServerExplorer, WMTSServerExplorer

    public interface DataServerExplorer
extends Disposable, DataFactoryUnit
    DataServerExplorer is an abstraction for any type of data server. It allows connecting to the server and browsing its contents. More specifically, this interface provides a list of the available data stores in a server.
